TW: before & after pic, ribs, body dysmorphia // i lost my period for 2 years and finally got it back in 2022 :,) i went on an intentional weight gain journey this year but also gained self-acceptance, trust in my body, and 4” inches in my glutes biiitch!! 

the weight that i carried was not sustainable for me. i existed through myfitnesspal & never thought i was lean enough, even in the before photos with my ribs showing (hi body dysmorphia). i was tired all the time, woke up at 3-4 am and went full send with preworkout and fasted lifts, and had no mf’in sex drive :,( i wish this was talked about more in the fitness industry

anyways i’m just eating without counting calories, being 🦄y, training for strength aka to hip thrust catapult loved ones out a burning building, and learning more about my body every day. can’t wait to see what 2023 has in store for me 💪🏻🥹
